item.title: GM Analysis #9: Williams vs Dragun: Sicilian Wing Gambit 2 b4!?
item.description:
GM Analysis #9: Williams vs Dragun: Sicilian Wing Gambit 2 b4!?

In this video I take a look at a game I played against the young Polish Grandmaster Kamil Dragun. I played the super aggressive Sicilian Wing Gambit, with 2 b4!? and got a very promising position. It was certainly fun, but did I win? * Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/pages/Ginger...
